title: Nilima's Snack Meal Service - Food Truck
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Fast food, Take-out
description: Food trailer serving vegetarian Indian food lunch meals, snacks, sweets, and drinks; is a licensed commercial kitchen facility. Its changing menu includes curries, whole wheat naan, basmati rice, mixed veggies, fried potato dumplings, veggie fritters, samosas. Also operates Saturday at Stillwater Farmer's Market in Strickland Park.
